stion%20de%20l%E2%80%99infrastructure%20r%C3%A9seau/SP1.html#recapitulatif-synthetique","title":"R\u00e9capitulatif synth\u00e9tique","text":"Sous-r\u00e9seau Adresse r\u00e9seau Masque Diffusion Passerelle Production 172.40.0.0/24 255.255.255.0 172.40.0.255 172.40.0.254 Autres 172.40.1.0/25 255.255.255.128 172.40.1.127 172.40.1.126 Administratif 172.40.1.128/25 255.255.255.128 172.40.1.255 172.40.1.254 Ventes / \u00c9tudes 172.40.2.0/26 255.255.255.192 172.40.2.63 172.40.2.62 Logistique 172.40.2.64/26 255.255.255.192 172.40.2.127 172.40.2.126 Serveurs 172.16.5X.0/24 255.255.255.0 172.16.5X.255 172.16.5X.253"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html","title":"Cr\u00e9er une documentation avec MkDocs et GitHub Pages","text":""},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#preparation-des-prerequis","title":"Pr\u00e9paration des pr\u00e9requis","text":""},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#1-installer-git","title":"1. Installer Git","text":""},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#linux-debian-ubuntu","title":"Linux (Debian / Ubuntu)","text":"<pre><code>sudo apt update\nsudo apt install git -y\n````\n\n#### macOS\n\n```bash\nbrew install git\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#windows","title":"Windows","text":"<p>T\u00e9l\u00e9charger et installer : https://git-scm.com/downloads</p> <p>V\u00e9rification :</p> <pre><code>git --version\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#2-installer-python","title":"2. Installer Python","text":""},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#linux-debian-ubuntu_1","title":"Linux (Debian / Ubuntu)","text":"<pre><code>sudo apt install python3 python3-pip -y\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#macos","title":"macOS","text":"<pre><code>brew install python\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#windows_1","title":"Windows","text":"<p>T\u00e9l\u00e9charger et installer : https://www.python.org/downloads/</p> <p>\u26a0\ufe0f Cocher Add Python to PATH</p> <p>V\u00e9rification :</p> <pre><code>python --version\npip --version\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#3-installer-mkdocs-et-le-theme-material","title":"3. Installer MkDocs et le th\u00e8me Material","text":"<pre><code>pip install mkdocs mkdocs-material\n</code></pre> <p>V\u00e9rification :</p> <pre><code>mkdocs --version\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#creation-du-projet-de-documentation","title":"Cr\u00e9ation du projet de documentation","text":""},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#4-creer-un-depot-github","title":"4. Cr\u00e9er un d\u00e9p\u00f4t GitHub","text":"<ol> <li> <p>Cr\u00e9er un d\u00e9p\u00f4t GitHub public (exemple : <code>ma-documentation</code>)</p> </li> <li> <p>Cloner le d\u00e9p\u00f4t :</p> </li> </ol> <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/&lt;user&gt;/ma-documentation.git\ncd ma-documentation\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#5-initialiser-mkdocs","title":"5. Initialiser MkDocs","text":"<pre><code>mkdocs new .\n</code></pre> <p>Structure obtenue :</p> <pre><code>.\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 docs/\n\u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 index.md\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 mkdocs.yml\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#redaction-de-la-documentation","title":"R\u00e9daction de la documentation","text":""},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#6-ecrire-le-contenu-markdown","title":"6. \u00c9crire le contenu Markdown","text":"<p>Modifier le fichier <code>docs/index.md</code> :</p> <pre><code># Bienvenue\n\nBienvenue dans la documentation de mon projet.\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip install mon-projet\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#utilisation","title":"Utilisation","text":""},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#7-configurer-le-site","title":"7. Configurer le site","text":"<pre><code>Modifier le fichier `mkdocs.yml` :\n\n```yaml\nsite_name: Ma Documentation\nsite_url: https://&lt;user&gt;.github.io/ma-documentation\n\ntheme:\n  name: material\n\nnav:\n  - Accueil: index.md\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#previsualisation-locale","title":"Pr\u00e9visualisation locale","text":""},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#8-lancer-le-serveur-local","title":"8. Lancer le serveur local","text":"<pre><code>mkdocs serve\n</code></pre> <p>Acc\u00e9der \u00e0 l\u2019adresse :</p> <pre><code>http://127.0.0.1:8000\n</code></pre> <p>Le site se met \u00e0 jour automatiquement lors des modifications.</p>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#publication-sur-github-pages","title":"Publication sur GitHub Pages","text":""},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#9-publier-la-documentation","title":"9. Publier la documentation","text":"<pre><code>mkdocs gh-deploy\n</code></pre> <p>Cette commande :</p> <ul> <li> <p>G\u00e9n\u00e8re le site statique</p> </li> <li> <p>Cr\u00e9e la branche <code>gh-pages</code></p> </li> <li> <p>Active GitHub Pages automatiquement</p> </li> </ul>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#acces-a-la-documentation","title":"Acc\u00e8s \u00e0 la documentation","text":"<p>La documentation est accessible \u00e0 l\u2019adresse :</p> <pre><code>https://&lt;user&gt;.github.io/ma-documentation\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#bonnes-pratiques-markdown","title":"Bonnes pratiques Markdown","text":"<ul> <li> <p>Utiliser des titres hi\u00e9rarchis\u00e9s (<code>#</code>, <code>##</code>, <code>###</code>)</p> </li> <li> <p>Ajouter des exemples de code</p> </li> <li> <p>Documenter chaque \u00e9tape</p> </li> </ul> <p>Exemple de note (th\u00e8me Material) :</p> <pre><code>!!! note\n    Ceci est une note importante.\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2-Cr%C3%A9er%20une%20documentation%20avec%20MkDocs%20et%20GitHub%20Pages.html#ressources","title":"Ressources","text":"<ul> <li> <p>MkDocs : https://www.mkdocs.org</p> </li> <li> <p>Material for MkDocs : https://squidfunk.github.io/mkdocs-material/</p> </li> <li> <p>GitHub Pages : https://pages.github.com</p> </li> </ul>"},{"location":"Documentations/SP2-Gestion%20du%20parc%20informatique/SP2.html","title":"A suivre...","text":""}]}